title: run with rundll32
extract: Help information is provided for a specific DLL you run with the rundll32 command. You must run the rundll32 command from an elevated command prompt. To open an elevated command prompt, click Start, right-click Command Prompt, and then click Run as administrator.Oct 15, 2017
